Articles.Content:
If any of you played Wing Commander Privateer, you probably encountered these Confederation ships patrolling various sectors. The F-71 Stiletto is said to be fast and agile, making it a formidable fighter. However, it's lightly armored and has light armament. This is one of the few ships that is capable of full SSTO. This thing will ascend after it runs off the other end of the runway.

Javascript is disabled. View full album
